{"tid":1471904,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"是日笑話：無腦藍絲","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:21:09.000Z","uid":208536,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf6c0c4080af396438165724558b1d5b8353156","tid":1471904,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:47:01.000Z","msg":"平日 我個深藍老豆都好少係屋企同我地正面開火<br />\n因為我老母係港豬<br />\n家姐淺藍 小弟勇武<br />\n<br />\n咁今晚突然 佢自己講出口<br />\n話佢同樓下啲啊嬸啊婆啊伯傾計<br />\n有個啊婆話<br />\n原來示威者真係有錢收<br />\n<br />\n咁我問番佢 人地講你又信<br />\n你個仔講你又唔信？<br />\n佢又知真？ 邊到聽番黎咋？<br />\n<br />\n佢當堂好似已經贏撚左咁講<br />\n佢啊 個日去維園遊行<br />\n有人行埋黎同佢講 3舊水 乜都唔洗做<br />\n坐就得<br />\n<br />\n聽到依到<br />\n個下我心諗 唔係真係有on9仔俾錢啊？<br />\n又真係咁on9俾人知啊？<br />\n點知下一句佢語出驚人<br />\n驚天地 泣鬼神 岩細佬 岩大人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個日維園班白衫啊 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&gt;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆你個街當堂笑到上氣唔接下氣<br />\n係Google 搵番守護香港個日啲新聞俾佢睇<br />\n佢望都唔敢望<br />\n仲要加多句<br />\n唉唔同你地講 講黎棧嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記得平心靜氣同佢地傾 聽佢地講 逐點逐點擊破"},{"pid":"bad35908ed4338c19d8c0a233d10cf312e9d2b14","tid":1471904,"uid":208536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:48:05.000Z","msg":"仆街上面打錯字 家姐係淺黃"},{"pid":"433a7a41531d76f62052231fab45f99b694ebfa3","tid":1471904,"uid":208536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:50:34.000Z","msg":"大家仲有無啲無腦藍絲既笑話分享下"},{"pid":"87cd01a24dcbc9e77c358a17b4beda66895a9b53","tid":1471904,"uid":51790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"藍屍=on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14022ed93dc5878896f6b34e78535a6dc330eb5f